Class AttributeHtmlTag

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.JspTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.Tag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.TryCatchFinally, ContainedTagInterface
public class AttributeHtmlTag
extends BaseTag

Attribute tag, tries to define attribute of the containing tag (element). First searches for HTML element from PageContext under the AttributedTagInterface.HTML_ELEMENT_KEY and if it is found writes out javascript that should set elements attribute. When this does not succeed, searches AttributedTagInterface.ATTRIBUTED_TAG_KEY and tries to attach attribute to found AttributedTagInterface, if any. This only works when AttributedTagInterface has been implemented correctly by containing tag and whole HTML for containing tag is written out in doEndTag() method.
